ant-safari/\'>Willem Larsen</a>\"',NULL,'iteration, project, release','All',NULL),(131,131,5,'Long','\"<a href=\'https://twitter.com/ani_angelini\'>Ani Angelini</a>\"',NULL,'iteration, project, release','All',NULL),(132,132,5,'Medium','<a href=\'https://www.xing.com/profile/KatrinElise_Dreyer\' target=\'_blank\'>Katrin Dreyer</a>',NULL,NULL,'Norming, Performing, Stagnating',NULL),(133,133,1,'Medium','Adapted by <a href=\'https://www.xing.com/profile/KaiAlexander_Lohr\' target=\'_blank\'>Kai Alexander Lohr</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(134,134,4,'Short','<a href=\'https://twitter.com/thorbenheins\' target=\'_blank\'>Thorben Heins</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(135,135,1,'Long','<a href=\'https://nomad8.com/how-to-avoid-waste-a-lean-retrospective/\' target=\'_blank\'>Tony O\'Halloran</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(136,136,0,'Short','Unknown via <a href=\'https://www.foryouandyourcustomers.com/mensch/andreas-drexhage/\' target=\'_blank\'>Andreas Drexhage</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(137,137,1,'Short','<a href=\'https://twitter.com/Yuliana_Step\' target=\'_blank\'>Juliana Stepanova</a>, inspired by the Play4Agile Orga Team',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(138,138,4,'Short','<a href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/cscaswell/\'>Chris Caswell</a> and <a href=\'https://www.kilearning.net/\'>Julian Kea</a>',NULL,'WithoutFacilitator','All',NULL),(139,139,1,'Medium','<a href=\'https://corinna-baldauf.de\'>Corinna Baldauf</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(140,140,0,'Short','Unknown via Corinna Baldauf',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(141,141,1,'Medium','<a href=\'https://twitter.com/PanzerDominik\'>Dominik Panzer</a>',NULL,NULL,'Performing, Stagnating, Adjourning','https://retromat.org/blog/#URL-EXAMPLE-ONLY-PUT-IN-SOMETHING-BETTER'),(142,142,1,'Medium','<a href=\'https://www.leadventure.de/\'>Sabina Lammert</a>','<a href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/sabina-lammert-14abb512b_projektmanagement-agile-projekt-activity-6823506455124045825-vaIs/\'>Original Post on LinkedIn</a>',NULL,'Storming, Performing',NULL),(143,143,0,'Short','<a href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/anh-bui-graphicrecording_wie-voll-ist-dein-energiefass-ugcPost-6787654857244389376-9Omz/\'>Anh Bui</a>',NULL,NULL,'All',NULL),(144,144,4,'Medium','<a href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefanie-dinh-144731194/\'>Stefanie Dinh</a>',NULL,NULL,'Adjourning',NULL),(145,145,2,'Long','<a href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/johanna-amlacher/\'>Johanna Amlacher</a>',NULL,'iteration, release','All',NULL),(146,146,1,'Long','<a href=\'https://www.role-up.com/resources/retrospective-roles-and-responsibilities\'>Role-Up</a>',NULL,NULL,'Storming',NULL);
